item.title: About
item.description: Who is BitsForEveryone? BitsForEveryone is a group consisting of current cadets, old grads, and civilians at the United States Military Academy. Who is C3T? Within BitsForEveryone is the Cadet Competitive Cyber Team (C3T), consisting of 20 cadets with 1 captain, 5 category champions, 14 other members, and a multitude of instructors and coaches. When BitsForEveryone competes in CTF competitions, C3T is behind the scenes working through West Point’s Cyber Research Center.
